    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 47-5-158, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE COMPOSITION OF THE INMATE WELFARE FUND COMMITTEE TO INCLUDE THE CHAIRPERSONS OF THE HOUSE AND SENATE CORRECTIONS COMMITTEES AND THE CHAIRPERSONS OF THE HOUSE AND SENATE ACCOUNTABILITY, EFFICIENCY AND TRANSPARENCY COMMITTEES AS NONVOTING MEMBERS; TO REQUIRE THE COMMITTEE TO MEET AT LEAST ONCE QUARTERLY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
